> A data quality, drift detection, and AI insights platform built with FastAPI, PostgreSQL, and Streamlit.

Transforms raw CSV datasets into structured insights with automated profiling, validation, drift detection, and optional AI-powered analysis.

---

## 🚀 Core Capabilities

### 📊 Data Profiling Engine
- Row and column statistics
- Missing value detection
- Duplicate row detection
- Memory usage estimation
- Automatic type inference

---

### 🧠 Data Quality Engine
- Column health scoring system
- Detects fully null columns
- Flags high missing rate columns (>30%)
- Identifies schema issues (Unnamed columns)

---

### 🔄 Dataset Drift Detection
- Schema drift (added / removed columns)
- Type drift (data type changes)
- Distribution drift (mean / std shifts)
- Dataset size changes over time

---

### 🤖 AI Insights (Optional)
- GPT-powered dataset analysis
- Risk detection
- Cleaning recommendations
- Graceful fallback when API is unavailable

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

Streamlit Frontend  
→ FastAPI Backend  
→ Pandas Processing Layer  
→ PostgreSQL Database  
→ OpenAI API (optional AI layer)

---

## 📸 Dashboard Preview

| View | Description |
|------|------------|
| Upload | CSV upload interface |
| Health Score | Dataset quality summary |
| Column Health | Column-level diagnostics |
| Missing Values | Distribution visualization |

